2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses memory-efficient backpropagation techniques to reduce memory complexity of network training. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep learning and its application to medical image processing. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper discusses low memory neural networks. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with processing of medical images.
